user_text: Small but it is very versatile. They make everything from coffee and milkshakes to breakfast and dinner. I ordered the Puerto Rican Tripleta Sandwich and couldn't even finish it. It was delicious.
Whenever i am in the area i always stop by. I get the bacon cheese burger with everything on it. Or I get a cold sandwiches when I'm there. The place is clean, Great food, and great service! :)
